title: 393. Andy & DJ CTI: PayPal Stock Plummets, Top Doctor Warns Risk Of Cardiac Death & Nuclear War To Solve Climate Change
itunes:title: 393. Andy & DJ CTI: PayPal Stock Plummets, Top Doctor Warns Risk Of Cardiac Death & Nuclear War To Solve Climate Change
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss PayPal's stock plummeting after the Daily Wire exposed a shocking misinformation policy, Florida's top doctor encouraging 18-39 year old men against the COVID vaccine due to an increased risk of cardiac death, and the Newsweek article claiming that a nuclear war could help prevent climate change.
